These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Food: nectarine, asparagus
Movie-Genre: adventure, sports
1. Movie-Genre:adventure is in an even position##4
2. Movie-Genre:sports == Food:asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Food   | asparagus | nectarine |
| Movie-Genre     | sports    | adventure   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Music-Genre: salsa, gospel
Food: grapefruit, artichoke
1. Food:grapefruit is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:gospel is on the left of Music-Genre:salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | salsa        |
| Food      | grapefruit  | artichoke |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Job: librarian, freelancer
Color: apricot, orange
1. Color:apricot is in an odd position##4
2. Job:freelancer is on the left of Job:librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Job   | freelancer    | librarian |
| Color   | apricot | orange |

